  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Mango auctioned for one million rupees",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An event took place in Vavunia where three mangoes and a garland were auctioned for one million rupees.",
        "The sixth day of the Sri Siddhivinayakar Temple Decoration Festival, located at Vavuniya Marakkarambalai Road, Ganesapuram, was held on 21st August.",
        "On that day, three mangoes and a wreath offered to the Lord were auctioned. Amid fierce competition, a student named Sabarirajan auctioned them for one million rupees.",
        "The incident of mangoes being auctioned for such a huge amount in a rural temple has left everyone in awe. The temple management said that the money raised in the auction will be used for the development of the temple."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
